{"tid":2351901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"河南直擊「孤兒雜技團」血與淚 23童忍痛練功：只為有個家","createTime":"2021-01-03T15:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T15:44:56.000Z","uid":71215,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbdc7561aca50fb9bd7c15d41ee95e01670bdb30","tid":2351901,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=87PsENlQdt8&amp;ab_channel=%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%8B%95%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9EHKAppleDaily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D87PsENlQdt8%26ab_channel%3D%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259EHKAppleDaily&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0JKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=0d5515fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=87PsENlQdt8&amp;ab_channel=%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%8B%95%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9EHKAppleDaily</a><br />\n河南濮陽是中國雜技之鄉，當地一個「孤兒雜技團」備受關注，團長劉甫曾坐牢，出獄後行善專收孤兒或單親家庭、窮困家庭小孩，甚至殘疾兒童練雜技。《蘋果》記者近日赴當地直擊團中23名5歲半至15歲孩童，他們不怕食住簡陋，最怕練功，但哭完抹去眼淚仍堅持繼續學，理由只有1個：「能有一技傍身，賺錢養家！」<br />\n<br />\n劉甫帶領的濮善雜技團，居無定所，試過將公園當練功地，如今暫時棲身濮縣夜市改成的基地，掛上濮善藝術培訓中心的招牌，算有了自家空地練功，但住的是貨櫃屋，周圍是粟米田。23名學員逼在同一間房，睡牀用多個碌架牀拼成。他們每周練功6日，只有周日休息。早上5點幾起身，先在基地跑20圈，然後梳洗，休息完7點半在食堂外列隊，背誦感恩詞後吃早餐。每周六日上午8點到10點半、下午3點到5點半練習基本功，包括翻筋斗和拉筋動作。<br />\n<br />\n脫貧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11e2d389631985a900ef6b0d709840a4f8d9975","tid":2351901,"uid":158974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"鐵華團<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065bb44277a6610e78f87bfd4d04c8fa4ab5d521","tid":2351901,"uid":301989,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 賤種幼蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2d129418f83cfcd075dcbd794a6b0240473585","tid":2351901,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"練完功夫去打洋鬼子"},{"pid":"703f8e6df2fa6aed70af57747dc60c65091098b0","tid":2351901,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:40:59.000Z","msg":"幸福中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a66881164d2649deb250eaad8e31a43163eddab","tid":2351901,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:41:52.000Z","msg":"喺支那鬼國 <br />\n練嚟把撚<br />\n<br />\n刷首抽啦"},{"pid":"ad84a18414064a1f61ebdb6d714921dfd2a84afe","tid":2351901,"uid":69737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"霸王別姬2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}